values: It's been pretty much 8000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000 years since I've last posted, so I just thought I'd leave people with an update. Some highlights of my past month: -Meeting Shew and Murdy, the latter of which is still here, and will be here till August the 15th. That's why I'm never online lately! -Otakon, which was amazing! Dancing, meeting the Ghey family + Connor + Nancy, all the AAA goodness such as meeting Nishi + the rest, and getting to hug and kiss him >D Why yes I got fresh with him! I couldn't help myself! D: Things were kind of all over china for a little bit, I was happy but pissy but sort of emo at the same time- now everything is better, though. It'll be a LOT better when I get to be online and talk to Shew normally, and we can call RP and everything will be cool. It's been awhile since I've gotten to really talk to her without being all ASHGISHGIHASG, and I'm looking forward to it. I want you to know that I still value you as a friend, and I still care a LOT for you. I miss talking to you! ToT I hope things can be cool between us, even despite what happened. You're a really close friend of mine, closer than a LOT, and I definitely don't want to lose that. But anyway- it's almost my birthday! OMG August 10th! People should send me birthday cards/presents, wahahaha! I kid! Sort of :D' But anyway- maybe Sunday we're going to Spedie fest, and Tuesday, we are going to Dorney park with Adrian's church. It's going to be a good time ^o^ I don't really know what's going on after that... I suppose I'll find out when those days get here! ^o^ I hope everyone has a really good time while I'm gone, I'll miss you all! ToT I'll be back online soon! <3333333 Love you all! Sumi p.s: I think I'm going to make another LJ... One which can fit all of my moods. This one is so pink and girly >.o Haha p.s.s: My Jay muse misses his HeeChul! Even if his anae does have rediculously short hair!
Waffles + George Michaels = Best moment of my life.

Baby beluga in the deep blue sea, Swim so wild and you swim so free, Heaven above and the sea below, And a little white whale on the go. Baby beluga, baby beluga, Is the water warm? Is your mama home, With you, so happy. Way down yonder where the dolphins play, Where you dive and splash all day, Waves roll in and the waves roll out, See the water squirtin' out of your spout. Baby beluga, oh baby beluga, Sing your little song, Sing for all your friends, We like to hear you. When it's dark, and you're home and fed, Curl up snug in your water bed. Moon is shining and the stars are out, Good night, little whale, good night. Baby beluga, baby beluga, With tomorrow's sun, another day's begun, You'll soon be waking. Baby beluga in the deep blue sea, Swim so wild and you swim so free. Heaven above and the sea below, And a little white whale on the go. You're just a little white whale on the go. p.s: Blame this entry on Shew XDDD'
